headline: Molina Healthcare (MOH) Sees 20% Stock Price Increase Over Last Month
summary: Molina Healthcare (MOH) recently reported a significant monthly price move of 20%, despite a mixed overall stock market performance. While the Dow Jones Industrial Average experienced a slight decline, the tech-focused Nasdaq reached new highs, reflecting broader confidence in certain market sectors. headline: Elevance Health Shrinks to Grow Stronger: From Part D to Plan B?
summary: ELV exits Part D and trims Medicare Advantage markets, betting on stronger-margin plans to protect profitability.
